OL,3,CPersonal stylists and confidence
OL,4,Csessions - how women are getting back
OL,5,Cto work
OL,7,FAmy Sutton went to find out more about
OL,8,Fhow Smart Works is helping to give
OL,9,Fwomen confidence - and helping them
OL,10,Ffind a job.
OL,12,FOffering personal stylists and
OL,13,Finterview coaching, a North East
OL,14,Fcharity is helping hundreds of women
OL,15,Fget back into work.
OL,17,FSmart Works Newcastle, an employment
OL,18,Fcharity based in the city, says
OL,19,Ffinding work has become significantly
OL,20,Fharder for women in the region over
OL,21,Fthe past year.
