OL,4,Csessions - how women are getting back
OL,5,Cto work
OL,7,FIt has been working across the North
OL,8,FEast for six years and has just opened
OL,9,Fa new centre which it hopes will help
OL,10,Fit increase the number of women it is
OL,11,Fhelping.
OL,13,FOffering interview coaching, peer
OL,14,Fsupport and assisting women with
OL,15,Fprofessional workwear, the charity has
OL,16,Fseen demand for its services increase
OL,17,Fthis year.
OL,19,FIn the last four months alone it has
OL,20,Fhelped 280 people - an increase of 100
OL,21,Ffrom the previous year.
