OL,7,FIts goal is to help 1,000 a women a
OL,8,Fyear into employment.
OL,10,FSophie Milliken, chair of Smart Works,
OL,11,Fsaid: "It's a very needed service.
OL,12,FUnfortunately we have higher than
OL,13,Faverage unemployment rates in our
OL,14,Fregion.
