OL,3,CPersonal stylists and confidence
OL,4,Csessions - how women are getting back
OL,5,Cto work
OL,7,F"We find, on average, a woman who is
OL,8,Faccessing our service has applied for
OL,9,F33 jobs before securing one interview.
OL,10,FThat is insane - I don't think I've
OL,11,Fapplied for 33 jobs in my life.
OL,12,FImagine how lacking in confidence you
OL,13,Fwould feel.
OL,15,F"We're a very small charity but we're
OL,16,Fpunching above our weight."
OL,18,FThe charity gets referrals from
OL,19,Fwomen's shelters, mental health
OL,20,Fcharities, employment schemes and job
OL,21,Fcentres.
