OL,7,FAmong the services it offers are the
OL,8,Fchance to practise interviews and have
OL,9,Fa personal stylist help women find
OL,10,Fsuitable clothes.
OL,12,FDragons Den entrepreneur Sara Davies,
OL,13,Fwho is an ambassador, opened the new
OL,14,Fcentre at Hadrian House Newcastle on
OL,15,FMonday 9 September.
