OL,7,FMs Davies, who ran the Great North Run
OL,8,Fthis year for the charity, said: "I
OL,9,Fdress all the time as a reflection of
OL,10,Fme because I know that when I've got
OL,11,Fthat bit of imposter syndrome, when
OL,12,FI'm not feeling it, I can put the
OL,13,Fclothes on and I can almost, not hide
OL,14,Fbehind them but it can make me feel a
OL,15,Fcertain way.
OL,17,F"That makes me act a certain way which
OL,18,Fwill get me to where I want to be."
