OL,7,FShe added: "There are so many
OL,8,Fdifferent reasons that women might be
OL,9,Fout of work.
OL,11,F"It's sad that the service is needed
OL,12,Fmore than ever but it's brilliant that
OL,13,Fthe North East community has risen to
OL,14,Fthe challenge and said how can we come
OL,15,Fout in force to really be there for
OL,16,Fthose women."
