OL,7,FClaire Meadows, volunteer stylist,
OL,8,Fsaid: "It's so important. Some of the
OL,9,Fsteps these women have to go through
OL,10,Fto get that interview or to get
OL,11,Fchildcare cover even to come into the
OL,12,Fcentre.
OL,14,F"It's their moment that it's all about
OL,15,Fthem. For some of them it's been a
OL,16,Freally long time since they've had a
OL,17,Fmoment that's all about them."
